data.description: This Ranch sits on an oversized lot. Large back yard for family and friends. Meticulously maintained 4 bedroom 2 bath all brick ranch home with an attached garage. Large primary suite with a full bath and a walk-in closet. Great room with a gas fireplace. Open kitchen with stainless steel appliances. Formal dining and living rooms. Spacious bedrooms including a FROG. Huge utility room with built in cabinets, deep sink and room for an extra fridge. Peaceful screened in back deck, perfect for relaxing. Fenced in yard with a storage shed. Geothermal HVAC system. Conveniently located in the heart of Great Bridge. Truly a must see.
